BT /F1 10 Tf 54 499 Td (95% Wald CI computed on log\(PRR\). WHO-UMC signal criteria: PRR >= 2, chi^2 >= 4, n >= 3.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 485 Td (- Reporting Odds Ratio \(ROR\) also computed as \(a/b\) / \(c/d\) with 95% CI.) Tj ET
