BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602 Td (- FAERS reports are voluntary and subject to reporting bias. PRR detects) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588 Td (disproportionality in reporting, not incidence or causality.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574 Td (- Individual-level PHI must not be published. The repository should not include raw) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 560 Td (narratives or patient identifiers when shared publicly.) Tj ET
